Shugaban kasar Mexico Andrés Manuel López Obrador ya yi alkawarin cewa ba zai yi amfani da sojoji kan fararen hula ba.
Zababben shugaban kasar Mexico Andrés Manuel López Obrador ya sha alwashin ba zai taba amfani da sojoji kan fararen hula ba, yayin da kasar ke gab da cika shekaru 50 da kisan gillar da aka yi wa daliban.
A ranar Asabar a sansanin Tlatelolco, Lopez Obrador ya yi alkawarin cewa ba zai taba amfani da sojoji don zaluntar 'yan Mexico ba.
A ranar 2 ga Oktoba, 1968, a lokacin zanga-zangar lumana a harabar makarantar, sojojin sun harbe mutane kusan 300, yayin da 'yan makaranta na hagu suka yi ta yaduwa a Latin Amurka.
Lopez Obrador ya yi alkawarin taimaka wa matasa 'yan Mexico ta hanyar ba da tallafin wata ga waɗanda suke karatu da kuma kafa jami'o'i kyauta.
Ya ce rashin aikin yi da rashin ilimi suna sa matasa su zama 'yan daba.
Dole ne Amurka ta ninka kudaden da take bayarwa don kera fasaha.
"Yayin da China ke kara samun ci gaba a fannin kera kere, Amurka ta bukaci ninka kudaden da take kashewa wajen gudanar da bincike a fannin", in ji mai saka jari kuma masanin fasahar kere kere Kai-Fu Lin, wanda ya yi aiki da Google, Microsoft da Apple.
Wannan magana ta zo ne bayan da sassan gwamnatin Amurka suka yi magana game da AI, alhali Amurka ba ta da wata dabara ta AI.
A shekarar da ta gabata, kasar Sin ta gabatar da shirinta, da nufin zama kasa ta farko a fannin kera fasaha a shekarar 2030.
"Sau biyu a kasafin kudin bincike na AI kyakkyawan farawa ne, idan aka yi la'akari da cewa Amurka tana da matukar ci gaba a wasu ƙasashe, kuma muna jiran ci gaba na gaba a cikin AI", in ji Li.
