Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya fara yakin neman zabe a garin Wheeling na jihar West Virginia a daren yau.
Wannan shi ne na farko cikin gangami biyar da Trump ya shirya yi a mako mai zuwa, ciki har da tsayawa a wurare masu kyau, da suka hada da Tennessee da Mississippi.
An jinkirta zaben da za a yi domin cike gurbin da ke gaban kotun kolin Amurka, kuma Trump na neman samun goyon baya a zaben da ake shirin yi a tsakiyar shekara, yayin da 'yan Republican ke gab da rasa iko a kan majalisar dokoki, yayin da za a fara kidaya kuri'un a watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne za a yi taron Trump a West Virginia a yau, kuma ta yaya za a iya kallon taron a kan layi?
An shirya taron Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia a karfe 7 na yamma ET yau Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
