Ana sa ran Trump zai yi magana a kan sauraron shari'ar da za a yi a wannan makon game da takarar kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ya zama abin damuwa saboda zargin cin zarafin jima'i, wanda ya kawo jinkirin da majalisar dattijai ta yi na kada kuri'ar tabbatarwa har zuwa mako guda kafin hukumar ta FBI ta gudanar da bincike.
Amma babban manufar wannan gangamin shi ne taimaka wa 'yan Republican da ke fuskantar zaben watan Nuwamba su samu karfin gwiwa.
A sakamakon haka, kamfen din shugaba Trump ya ce gangamin zabe biyar da za a yi a mako mai zuwa na neman karfafa masu aikin sa kai da magoya baya, yayin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin karewa da kuma fadada rinjaye da suke da shi a majalisar dattawa da majalisar wakilai, Reuters ta ruwaito.
"Sarrafa majalisar dokoki yana da matukar muhimmanci ga ajandar shugaban kasa, don haka zai ziyarci jihohi da dama kamar yadda zai iya yayin da muke shiga cikin yakin neman zabe", in ji wani mai magana da yawun Trump, wanda ya yi jinkirin bayyana sunansa, a cewar Reuters.
Taron da aka shirya a filin wasa na Wessex Arena a yau zai iya kawo magoya baya daga Ohio da Pennsylvania da kuma samun rahoto daga kafofin watsa labarai na Pittsburgh, a cewar West Virginia Metro News.
