Kuma yanzu ga wani yanki daga wannan Almanac na safiyar Lahadi. 30 ga Satumba, 1882 a yau, shekaru 136 da suka gabata, a wannan ranar ne aka haifi masanin kimiyyar lissafi Johannes Wilhelm Hans Giger a Jamus.
Giger ya kirkiro wata hanya ta ganowa da kuma auna radiyo, wani abu da ya haifar da Giger counter.
Wani lokaci jigon kimiyya, Giger counter ya zama jigon al'adun gargajiya, kamar yadda yake a cikin Coronado Bells, wanda ke nuna manyan mashahuran masanan kimiyya Roy Rogers da Dale Evans.
