An shirya sabuwar jirgin ruwan sojin ruwa na Jamus da za a kaddamar da shi a shekarar 2014 don maye gurbin jiragen yakin Cold War, amma ba za a iya yin hakan ba har zuwa karshen shekara saboda rashin ingantattun tsarin da kuma karuwar kudade, in ji kafofin watsa labarai na gida.
An jinkirta ƙaddamar da sabon jirgin ruwa na Rheinland-Pfalz, sabon jirgin ruwa na Baden-Wuerttemberg zuwa farkon rabin 2019, in ji wani mai magana da yawun soja, kamar yadda Die Zeit ta ruwaito.
An shirya jirgi ne don shiga cikin rundunar sojan ruwa a shekarar 2014, amma matsalolin da suka faru bayan samarwa sun hana aiwatar da wannan shiri mai ban sha'awa.
